{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e197bd31e2","title":"中共上海市委统战部关于“荣盛小集团”的问题的复查结论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"47780dbce1","index":0,"year":1984,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"e197bd31e2"}],"tags":[{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bc2c9b26b5","type":"title","text":"中共上海市委统战部关于“荣盛小集团”的问题的复查结论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e197bd31e2"},{"id":"4bccc147dc","type":"paragraph","text":"1957年整风反右期间，对荣毅仁等同志以“荣盛小集团”问题进行揭发批判是错误的。它严重损害了党和工商界上层人士的关系，破坏了工商界上层人士之间的团结，挫伤了这些同志的积极性。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e197bd31e2"},{"id":"40509fa191","type":"paragraph","text":"经复查，所谓“荣盛小集团”并不存在，这是反右扩大化的反映。为了彻底纠正“左”的错误，对1957年上海市民建，工商联“两会”常委会上批判的所谓“荣盛小集团”问题，予以彻底否定，有关材料予以销毁，并在相应的范围内肃清影响。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e197bd31e2"},{"id":"4abe8ea6fb","type":"paragraph","text":"中共上海市委统战部","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e197bd31e2"},{"id":"bc0b60d235","type":"paragraph","text":"1984年12月","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e197bd31e2"},{"id":"575e9edf62","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《荣毅仁》，北京：中央文献出版社。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e197bd31e2"}],"page":{"id":"db093cacda","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"e197bd31e2","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}